item.title: Competition Weekend Wrap Party
item.description: Celebrate the completion of your film with your team at Novo Brazil, Mission Valley, and tell war stories to your fellow film makers over food and drink.

item.title: Competition Weekend Kickoff
item.description: The start of the 2024 San Diego 48 Hour Film Project competition weekend, we meet at NTC Park Liberty Station… where genres are picked, and random elements are assigned.

item.title: Last Chance Mixer
item.description: The last 48 Hour Film Project mixer / meet & greet of the 2024 competition year at Mujeres Brew House, Barrio Logan

item.title: 2024 Open Auditions
item.description: An open audition for prospective 48 Hour Film Project actors, and teams that are casting acting talent
